{"tid":1982184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登啲討論越嚟越冇意義","createTime":"2020-04-21T05:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T20:17:59.000Z","uid":345458,"like":166,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"2feb79a1bbd7f2a120dd0e4f91e40281a4731eb5","tid":1982184,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:18:43.000Z","msg":"首先講返連登最近嘅討論風氣先：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>1. 飛機文大量出現</ins></span></span><br />\n越嚟越多啲好虛幻嘅Post...乜嘢如果有三戰會走去邊逃難...黑警同美軍海豹部隊巷戰...大佬而家廿一世紀啦，二戰之後教訓仲唔夠多咩，仲開戰？現實啲啦好冇？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>2. 新聞Post比例大增</ins></span></span><br />\n唔知由幾時開始少咗策略/行動Post，幾乎成個熱門都係新聞。就好似今日金正恩單野，真係值得討論咩？就算要討論都等有可靠消息披露先討論啦，仲要三個相關Post同時喺熱門，唔識自己上網睇新聞？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">以上呢啲風氣只會令個討論氣氛更加差，對場社運冇好處，以下係解決方法：</span><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 停止圍爐打飛機</span><br />\n本身連登影響力已經低咗好多，身邊都已經冇咩frd睇連登，再唔停止打飛機，現實啲嘅連登已經冇任何價值。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">2. 多返啲行動/策略/社評Post</span><br />\n太多新聞Post只會不斷減少大家嘅思考同反思空間，一定要正視。選舉冇人討論，黃色經濟圈大把黃店吿急冇人討論，工會戰線冇人討論，根本係浪費緊呢個咁好嘅平台。"},{"pid":"a763fb817f143fe586216ba7ae2586f5256212be","tid":1982184,"uid":345458,"like":17,"dislike":12,"score":5,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:19:51.000Z","msg":"不能理解連登仔唸緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4f3bd9b2c6db01757733cab9cda4d7756dedc9","tid":1982184,"uid":177213,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:19:57.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5266e5633499aef57f9efa97f6cf9ee601c5cec3","tid":1982184,"uid":177213,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a763fb817f143fe586216ba7ae2586f5256212be","tid":1982184,"uid":345458,"like":17,"dislike":12,"score":5,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:19:51.000Z","msg":"不能理解連登仔唸緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:20:16.000Z","msg":"證明你係正常人一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca7a0a71eedd1465b8e583dd09ce93b632e0b8d0","tid":1982184,"uid":292151,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:21:09.000Z","msg":"有行動post但係唔夠人推咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b883c193dd3a5c66e453a180140019f5490d2e3d","tid":1982184,"uid":81273,"like":11,"dislike":22,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:21:10.000Z","msg":"好多pr公司五毛搞亂連登<br />\n時事台貼乜撚新聞"},{"pid":"80e62db757070a49f950d43e6290abf13d744179","tid":1982184,"uid":153239,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:21:15.000Z","msg":"你望下D新聞Post你就會見到以前D出名五毛既名<br />\n佢地大多數就丟低 D字就算 然後乜都唔回<br />\n<br />\n同埋出現一D意義不明既韓星J圖POST<br />\n呢家連登最多係發布資訊既平台, 討論次要"},{"pid":"72ad857b96b00c2552ce10b2caf93836969f480f","tid":1982184,"uid":53062,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:21:27.000Z","msg":"時事台討論新聞都唔得<br />\n行動策略Post 照道理係去活動台"},{"pid":"774ed3f043a59708af5a103bb9d1cdea0b1a7c1f","tid":1982184,"uid":54291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:22:36.000Z","msg":"金正恩真係無咩咁重要"},{"pid":"e1200758c36481868bbd377171ffefaa9db43496","tid":1982184,"uid":345458,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"72ad857b96b00c2552ce10b2caf93836969f480f","tid":1982184,"uid":53062,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:21:27.000Z","msg":"時事台討論新聞都唔得<br />\n行動策略Post 照道理係去活動台"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:23:18.000Z","msg":"咁遊行Post係咪要Post去旅游台？"},{"pid":"d746ec4b572d3ae7bfcfde00656060819643b990","tid":1982184,"uid":45914,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:23:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5aae5b70f6d7492a8a045d349f4bad803745b1de","tid":1982184,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco